-- Aveng Finance Director Scott Resigns to Join Unidentified Platinum Company
-- Vernon Wessels
-- 2010-07-07T10:03:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-07/aveng-finance-director-scott-resigns-to-join-unidentified-platinum-company.html

          
          
             Aveng Ltd., the South African
construction company, said Financial Director Simon Scott will
leave the company on Sept. 26 to join a company involved in the
platinum mining industry.  
          
          


  


        